Package ca.mcgill.splendorclient.lobbyserviceio

Interface OutputParser

All Known Implementing Classes:
NullParser, Parsejson, ParseText
public interface OutputParser
Parses output. Singleton design pattern is well advised given that access to output parser will be requested from multiple, disparate places within the system and the implementation is same and so there can be benefits to only having one instance in existence.
